content: Dennis, if you want to change your Zoom background, hover over the three dots in the upper right hand corner of your picture and choose the option you want.  I will leave your question up in case you are looking for other types of help.  Thank you for being here!
Change zoom background by clicking the  ^ next to the Video button on the toolbar.
<@568257600228032512> Thanks, Carolyn.  As much as I use Zoom, I never paid attention to that fact.  It's my one new thing learned today!  üòç
